window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Book nine: summer in the Big Apple. Eight million stories of excitement and adventure...plus one. </p> <p>Declan O'Carroll is ready to start his summer internship at the hottest new company on the planet, Demidova Incorporated. What will he be doing? What tasks could he possibly handle for the most famous couple on Earth? After all, what could a second-semester college freshman hope to add to a multinational conglomerate? </p> <p>As the strongest male witch in existence, it might just be much, much more than anyone could ever predict. </p>"; 
